Package org.openscience.cdk.config.fragments

Class EStateFragments

java.lang.Object
org.openscience.cdk.config.fragments.EStateFragments
public class EStateFragments extends Object
A class representing the 79 E-state atom types in terms of SMARTS. These fragments were originally described in [Hall, L.H. and Kier, L.B. . Journal of Chemical Information and Computer Science. 1995. 35] and were converted into SMARTS forms by the RDKit project
